
'''Building Smart Communities through Network Weaving'''

URL = http://www.orgnet.com/BuildingNetworks.pdf

Key paper by Valdis Kreb and June Holley, which defines 4 phases in community network development:

   1. Scattered Clusters
   2. Single Hub-and-Spoke
   3. Multi-Hub Small-World Network
   4. Core/Periphery

